about.description:
Tools for the extraction of OpenStreetMap (OSM) street network data.
Intended to be used in tandem with Pandana and UrbanAccess libraries to
extract street network nodes and edges.
about.summary: Tools for the extraction of OpenStreetMap street network data for use in Pandana accessibility analyses.

name: osmnet
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.1.5" %}

package:
  name: osmnet
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/o/osmnet/osmnet-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 2fb96a7a95e34af45d1b8c5f88705da6876143820781220b1f55adf1f242639e

build:
  number: 3
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - requests >=2.9.1
    - pandas >=0.16.0
    - numpy >=1.10
    - geopandas >=0.2.1
    - shapely >=1.5

test:
  imports:
    - osmnet

about:
  home: https://github.com/UDST/osmnet
  license: AGPL-3.0
  license_family: AGPL
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: 'Tools for the extraction of OpenStreetMap street network data for use in Pandana accessibility analyses.'
  description: |
    Tools for the extraction of OpenStreetMap (OSM) street network data.
    Intended to be used in tandem with Pandana and UrbanAccess libraries to
    extract street network nodes and edges.
  doc_url: https://udst.github.io/osmnet/
  dev_url: https://github.com/UDST/osmnet

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - pksohn
    - smmaurer
